snippet.textDisplay:
Have you ever felt so lost and helpless in your life that it seemed like there was no end to it?? This song is both a cry and a prayer from those lonesome souls. If anyone finds you shedding tears while listening to this song, just tell them it's probably just a grain of sand that got in your eye. Because the loneliness this song touches is so deep and pure that no one will ever understand, nor anyone else ever should. 

💙

Love for Coke Studio and the entire team from the core of my heart!

snippet.textDisplay:
বিষম নদীর পানি,
ঢেউ করে হানাহানি–
ভাঙা এ তরণী
তবু বাই রে ।।

জীবন যুদ্ধের এই রূপক পংক্তিগুলো হৃদয়ে তীরের মত বিঁধলো💔

Thanks for this heart touching rendition of the timeless song.
